Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.40,0:00:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a soldier 而那也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.63,0:00:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.87,0:00:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同时站在火线的两端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.48,0:00:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕过危险的转角追过生与死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.05,0:00:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奔向前挑战谎言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.89,0:00:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论编织出多少谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.53,0:00:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相还是会照出光明的轮廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.57,0:00:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.10,0:00:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们的痛苦都抛在脑后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.04,0:00:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.64,0:00:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.21,0:01:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是士兵不是站着就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.65,0:01:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.22,0:01:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.85,0:01:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它们留给审判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.12,0:01:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.69,0:01:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.46,0:01:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲的时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.16,0:01:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能奋起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.43,0:01:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻壳机动队 S.A.C. 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.52,0:01:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回家路上绕过去买
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.43,0:01:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.73,0:01:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道尺寸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.36,0:01:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——直接穿脱型的L SIZE 对吧 ——那是爸爸对吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.93,0:01:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——恩 ——妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.10,0:01:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.41,0:02:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.94,0:02:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要逃离开我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么眼神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.18,0:02:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把枪丢掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.76,0:02:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把痛觉切断了 没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.26,0:03:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤得怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.82,0:03:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么想找死吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.29,0:03:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#10 疯狂的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.46,0:04:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总共打了12发子弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.66,0:04:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个数字没错吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.10,0:04:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.30,0:04:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还得再拘留一阵子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是公安9课的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.35,0:04:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有可能要进行简式审判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.72,0:04:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.09,0:04:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是受你父母委托替你辩护的律师上田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.26,0:04:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能想办法尽快帮我换新的义体啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.83,0:04:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有痛觉却痛得受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.71,0:04:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两天内就可以出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.31,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 挨了那么多颗子弹一定很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.71,0:04:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实那不过是件意外对吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.78,0:04:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你改造过不少次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.02,0:05:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但把不同厂商的零件装在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.56,0:05:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次也都改写控制软体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.83,0:05:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.20,0:05:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是专门打义体相关案件的律师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此对这类事情非常熟悉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.77,0:05:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在一般情形下也有可能因为某种状况造成控制机能失常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.61,0:05:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起诉状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.95,0:05:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因左列案件提起公诉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2032年9月9日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.92,0:05:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新滨地方检察署检察官森和臣检事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新滨地方法院庭上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本籍 新滨县
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.50,0:05:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住所 新滨市住吉台2-B-5
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.93,0:05:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无职业的和泉胜彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.10,0:05:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2009年6月18日生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.37,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起诉事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.27,0:05:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被告对曾经交往过的新滨市市立医院护士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.18,0:05:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静野由加里 当时24岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.48,0:06:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数次要求复合却遭拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.02,0:06:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.02,0:06:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 你又不是犯人却遭到拘留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.46,0:06:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这是为了让审判能尽快结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.63,0:06:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且虽说是为了救人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.86,0:06:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实在执勤时间外开了枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是非带枪不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以辞去现在保全公司的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辞掉工作那我们一家四口吃什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.77,0:06:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长 抱歉让您专程过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情过去了就不要再提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.49,0:06:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行动也有值得称赞的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.20,0:06:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 问题在于你在下班时间开枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.47,0:06:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.74,0:06:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌犯的老爸是大公司的社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.74,0:07:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于担任辩护人的那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个在义体相关争讼土不择手段捞钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶名昭彰的检察官转任律师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.31,0:07:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会做好心理准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.62,0:07:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔离时的会面很可能成为反对诘问的材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后就交给你自己判断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.36,0:07:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.43,0:07:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 关于我内人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.43,0:07:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经跟她说旁听也会留下不好的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.37,0:07:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是回去比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后提醒你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.27,0:07:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你应该已经知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.21,0:07:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法庭内禁止任何通讯行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.08,0:07:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常波段的通讯还会被反追踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.22,0:07:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.12,0:07:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做答辩的准备吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托古萨先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查报告上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记载你集中射击和泉先生的肩膀及双脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是想阻止他的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.47,0:08:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面是这么记载的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.37,0:08:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么有必要开这么多枪呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.97,0:08:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌犯有做义体化又说切断了感觉器官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.11,0:08:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我觉得有必要让他完全无法行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.88,0:08:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得你说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.92,0:08:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚开始有出声制止嫌犯的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.79,0:08:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是犯人并没有放下枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.32,0:08:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从犯人手中取走凶器是遂行逮捕时的铁则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.93,0:08:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 让我们稍微改变一下看事情的角度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.60,0:08:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托古萨先生 你看过这个吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.47,0:08:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.41,0:08:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟我执勤时用的枪同一型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.28,0:08:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.45,0:08:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是MATEBA公司制自动左轮枪的复制品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你工作的地方全员都使用这把枪吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.72,0:08:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人使用SEBURO M5
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEBURO M5是一种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.09,0:09:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多可连射21发5.7mm子弹的自动武器吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.63,0:09:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你的枪却只有六发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.87,0:09:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得这实在太没效率了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.41,0:09:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托古萨先生 用这把枪的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.71,0:09:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子弹打完了该怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.48,0:09:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃弹壳 装填新的子弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.41,0:09:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对枪不熟悉所以想请您说明一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左轮和自动武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.59,0:09:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一种比较能够快速更换子弹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.89,0:09:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能一概而论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大致上是自动武器比较快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.10,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 左轮也有优点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托古萨先生 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.70,0:09:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要针对问题回答就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我这样问你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.54,0:09:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SEBURO和MATEBA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.97,0:09:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一种装填子弹比较快?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.28,0:09:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是SEBURO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.71,0:09:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.38,0:09:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在执行任务的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.78,0:09:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意选择没效率的枪来使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.09,0:10:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你工作的性质来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.06,0:10:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一件非常不自然的事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.19,0:10:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实有你说的这一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.10,0:10:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 左轮和自动武器不同 不会出现卡弹的情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.33,0:10:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不遇到太紧急的状况这样的装弹数也足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.24,0:10:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个理由没什么说服力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.97,0:10:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在就遇到这种状况了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.44,0:10:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲直接一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.58,0:10:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是因为自己的喜好才配带左轮的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.78,0:10:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.45,0:10:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES还是N0？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.12,0:10:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是因为喜好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我再请教一个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告书里面有提到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.46,0:10:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你执勤的时候把相当多时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花在射击训练上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.27,0:10:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是原本就把射击这个行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作兴趣嗜好来看呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.17,0:10:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.71,0:10:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托古萨先生的射击训练是否来自个人兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是辩方律师的臆测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.31,0:11:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个发言毫无根据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异议有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.92,0:11:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望辩方律师提出与本案直接相关的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.32,0:11:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.93,0:11:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 托古萨先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.63,0:11:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟您确认一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得您向和泉先生开枪时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.93,0:11:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说过什么话吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.84,0:11:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不记得的话就让我告诉你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.11,0:11:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对和泉先生大吼“那么想找死吗?”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.38,0:11:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行动选项当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.18,0:11:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括了杀死嫌疑犯的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这根本就只是抓人语病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.83,0:11:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证人 请你坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.46,0:11:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上和泉先生的身体四肢关节都被子弹击中...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确开枪打了嫌犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.33,0:11:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那是为了救女性被害人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.24,0:12:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子你完全没有反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.47,0:12:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要转移焦点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.14,0:12:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证人请你坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.68,0:12:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是审判长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.41,0:12:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?还顺利吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他相当愤慨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.70,0:12:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个律师意料之外的精明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.73,0:12:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是托古萨又不是被告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.24,0:12:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休庭前几乎就像是被告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密码通讯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.58,0:12:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他切换成自闭模式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.88,0:12:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没了解到我们跟他会面的意图啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.42,0:12:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托古萨虽然菜 但并不笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.99,0:12:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他早就察觉到我们打算做密码通讯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.96,0:12:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这表示他不想在法庭内使用卑鄙手段吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.73,0:12:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.90,0:13:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途开始就完全不看我们这边了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查查被告的底细
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.20,0:13:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 你继续旁听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也暂时先回本部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.81,0:13:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.54,0:13:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为托古萨先生有杀人的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.58,0:13:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.75,0:13:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在调查报告里托古萨先生这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.42,0:13:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“跟嫌犯对峙的时候”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.15,0:13:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我一眼就判断出这名男子全身都做过义体化”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托古萨先生的这段话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.39,0:13:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,违反义体安装者歧视禁止法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.90,0:13:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.07,0:13:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本案近乎固执的开枪方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.47,0:13:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以认为是来自他对义体安装者的歧视意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.61,0:13:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.97,0:13:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审判长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.17,0:13:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里引用义体安装者歧视禁止法根本是方向错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.71,0:13:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异议有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.55,0:13:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望辩方律师根据具体事实提出反论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.69,0:13:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.19,0:13:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.79,0:13:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想先谈托古萨先生特殊的工作环境之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.46,0:14:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再进一步说明他的具体行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.83,0:14:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托古萨执勤的公安9课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.83,0:14:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个完全由安装强化义体的成员所组成的特殊组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.47,0:14:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在义体人环绕的工作环境中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.74,0:14:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫长时间处在紧张状态下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.84,0:14:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对安装义体的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.01,0:14:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他或许会在无意间产生自卑感和歧视意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.39,0:14:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果这次事件就成为他内心黑暗面的发泄口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.92,0:14:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.12,0:14:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的发言也是辩方律师无根据的臆测之词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.50,0:14:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异议有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.67,0:14:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.14,0:14:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被告的终端机发现有趣的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.54,0:14:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪前一天动手术安装非法义体的存证信函
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那个能击败他们吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.48,0:14:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且也算是证据吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.72,0:15:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将巴特找到的情报转给检方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.86,0:15:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 楠检事想把9课拉上法庭的这条情报呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.40,0:15:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然上次逮捕药岛干事长时这个男人就有动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.27,0:15:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 本案看来背后有人操纵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.80,0:15:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.51,0:15:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楠查到9课的情报后 多半有人在他的名利心上煽风点火吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.45,0:15:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是合田吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真敢下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.19,0:15:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.06,0:15:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸什么时候回来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.43,0:15:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 什么时候回来呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何贵干?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.57,0:15:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在考虑对你提出民事诉讼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算威胁我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.61,0:15:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚我跟你的上司荒卷课长取得联系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.11,0:15:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真是个通情达理的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.91,0:16:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了交换我撤回对你的民事诉讼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.32,0:16:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎同意把事情归结到义体控制上的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.65,0:16:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长不可能接受这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.02,0:16:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请原谅我只能按照预定计划进行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.86,0:16:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 9课的人大概会很伤脑筋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管事情怎么发展我都没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.07,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托古萨先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.48,0:16:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人如果是肉身的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.18,0:16:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会开那么多枪吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.25,0:16:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然会采取不同的应对方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.02,0:16:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么在最近发生的事件中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.12,0:16:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想请教你隶属的公安9课所采取的具体应对方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.36,0:16:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近频频发生义体化难民所犯下的自杀炸弹攻击对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这些事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.77,0:16:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说公安9课密切参与调查行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.84,0:16:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.51,0:17:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连数天前的连续自杀炸弹攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.51,0:17:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也亲自去逮捕犯人这是事实吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.89,0:17:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对媒体进行情报管制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.79,0:17:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.62,0:17:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那个事件这里有一份提交给检察官的报告书副本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.63,0:17:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据这份报告书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.40,0:17:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托古萨先生在阻止义体化难民自爆的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.74,0:17:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然发出警告却没有开枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.41,0:17:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么对本案嫌犯和对那个意图自爆的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.75,0:17:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应对方式有这么大的差异?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.78,0:17:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很明显是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.22,0:17:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心里有歧视意识的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.19,0:17:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这次事件当中我一开始也对嫌犯发出警告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.63,0:17:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他所采取的行动完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想帮助向我求救的被害人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.24,0:18:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你没有办法证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.24,0:18:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不打算用这件事来审判你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.24,0:18:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是想证明本案是因为你的行为引发的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.22,0:18:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和泉先生在连续自杀攻击案件发生后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.52,0:18:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越常因为自身的义体化受到没有道理的误解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.39,0:18:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此为了让大家能够区别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.83,0:18:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案发前一天才刚去换成一眼就知道不是难民的义手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以这样掰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.27,0:18:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问话完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时休庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.12,0:18:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.09,0:18:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种阴谋诡诈的审判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.89,0:18:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过世的被害人无法瞑目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.19,0:19:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天辩方律师跟我会面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用民事诉讼威胁我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.43,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼我作证让审判以意外结案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我工作的地方执行特殊任务这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作反对诘问的对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.50,0:19:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是想逼我退缩的把戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.51,0:19:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这种威胁已经没用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.94,0:19:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.98,0:19:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我将在此辞去9课的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.42,0:19:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被一时的激情所驱使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.36,0:19:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个事件不是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.89,0:19:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我无法救回被害人也是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.16,0:19:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想对我提出民事诉讼就尽管来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.30,0:19:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过相对的我绝对不会逃避这个审判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.34,0:19:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在休庭中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证词请在开庭之后提出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.68,0:19:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.91,0:19:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把这些话说在前头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.05,0:19:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近跟义体普及率成正比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.82,0:20:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一类的审判也不断增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.29,0:20:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 听说在这当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.45,0:20:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个特定义体制造商为了隐瞒自己公司商品的缺陷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与检察官和律师勾结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.89,0:20:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行不公正的审判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.66,0:20:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因为工作性质自然对这类内幕十分熟悉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在既然决心辞去9课的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.57,0:20:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就打算说出一切真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你们也要有所觉悟喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带证人离开法庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.70,0:20:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.90,0:20:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来的真慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.97,0:20:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点也不高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.54,0:20:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是少校也不该擅自制作灵魂侵入钥匙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.51,0:20:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不服气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.18,0:21:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为你在那边毫无意义地主张幼稚的正义感啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.48,0:21:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那岂不是反效果吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.25,0:21:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.58,0:21:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来嫌犯已经暂时被判有罪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.55,0:21:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式审判也会确定有罪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.49,0:21:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校在那边让你说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.76,0:21:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是清查嫌犯辩护律师的帐户后所得到的内幕情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.60,0:21:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该很怕自己的秘密曝光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.77,0:21:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.01,0:21:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用这次事件企图打击9课的楠检事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.81,0:21:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该也会在自己与律师的关系曝光之前收手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.55,0:21:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楠检事是指那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.75,0:21:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.75,0:21:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次剧本恐怕是内厅的合田写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.89,0:21:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副导演是楠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.26,0:21:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角则是那个检察官转任的律师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.49,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.63,0:21:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我在法庭上争取正义还有什么意义?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.33,0:21:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的正义恐怕已经没有出场的机会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.77,0:21:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来被害人无法瞑目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.04,0:22:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 也许会有天谴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.14,0:22:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天谴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.02,0:22:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.02,0:22:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据刚刚得到的新闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.05,0:22:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为扯上义体安装者歧视禁止法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得审判方向引发大众注意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.99,0:22:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护士命案的辩护律师和被告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.73,0:22:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——把这台车废弃掉 ——在审判回家途中发生交通意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.30,0:22:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——书面资料也全部销毁掉喔 ——律师重伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.03,0:22:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被告的义体似乎严重受损
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.80,0:22:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人乘坐的车子在高速公路上行驶时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.87,0:22:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞到中央分隔岛导致翻车严重损坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.11,0:22:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上田律师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.32,0:22:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新滨地方明日放晴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.52,0:22:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会是万里晴空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.42,0:22:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.53,0:22:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——爸爸今天会回来吗? ——预计最高温29度 湿度70％
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.49,0:22:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——很快就会到家了 ——今晚应该是个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.76,0:22:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有如热带的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.98,0:23:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出我体内行星和星星的银河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.68,0:23:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着它们每一个都唱着同样宁静的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.26,0:23:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在现实当中从来没看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.23,0:23:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的美丽事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.53,0:23:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一点怀疑或恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.07,0:23:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到一个声音--醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.17,0:23:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字--然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.64,0:23:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我省视自身--醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.75,0:23:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光随时都围绕着我--时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.05,0:23:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.45,0:23:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去让这一切成真的--它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.49,0:24:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在躯壳里的美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.79,0:24:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到一个声音--醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.73,0:24:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字--然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.10,0:24:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我省视自身--醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.51,0:24:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光随时都围绕着我--时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.74,0:24:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.01,0:24:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去让这一切成真的--它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.08,0:24:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这个躯壳里
